FBIS4-44326 "drweu125_j_94006" FBIS-WEU-94-125 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Iraq's Tariq 'Aziz Meets With Pope John Paul II Iraq's Tariq 'Aziz Meets With Pope John Paul II JN2806175694 Baghdad INA in Arabic 1715 GMT 28 Jun 94 JN2806175694 Baghdad INA Arabic BFN [Text] Vatican City, 28 Jun (INA)--[Iraqi] Deputy Prime Minister Tariq 'Aziz met here today with His Holiness Pope John Paul II. The deputy prime minister explained Iraq's position with regard to Security Council resolutions and the importance of both honoring these resolutions and commitment to their implementation on the part of the Security Council. During the meeting, the pope emphasized the Vatican's position, which rejects the blockade, and expressed his sympathy with Iraq.
